Class DocumentCollectionBrowseRecord

All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable
public class DocumentCollectionBrowseRecord
extends BrowseRecord

DocumentCollectionBrowseRecords are records of all information necessary to identify a collection of documents. Minimally, this will be collections and series. Maximally this will be collection, series, and volume.

Constructor Summary
DocumentCollectionBrowseRecord(String collection, String series, Boolean isDocumentParent)

DocumentCollectionBrowseRecord(String collection, String series, String volume)
          Constructor for cases in which the volume is known Note that if a volume is known, the collection's children must be documents and not collections; i.e., isDocumentParent is true
